title: Mr Billy's
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, International, Western, British, European, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Friendly family-run cafe specializing in tea and coffees and locally sourced food. Most food is made-in-house. Soy milk is available for coffees. Offers one vegan cake on the set menu with others available. Staff has a good understanding of what vegan food is and are helpful. At least half the menu is vegetarian and at least two of these are either vegan or can be made vegan.
